---
title: Creole Pork & Roast Veggie Couscous with Almonds & Garlic Dip
description: Get ready to dig into a nutritious taste sensation. The fresh veggies, roasted to warm perfection are tossed through the lush bowl of couscous. Sitting on top is the tender creole-spiced pork. A chilled garlic dip dolloped on top will refresh you in no time.
